e":"2020-06-09T23:53:24.000Z","msg":"佢下一鋪一定係想攪美國既糧食。可能播毒毒晒美國既農作物"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"咁on9自己切斷自己糧食供應"},{"pid":"ba66f7fb00eeaa1d44300828e8fb985a89c783f3","tid":2057730,"uid":173945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:35:50.000Z","msg":"打仗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0dac82f8e114911c5dcb8c0a6d3010c10619654","tid":2057730,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"091edf9d6ca7a4df998c084303fb4177c7a9b7a7","tid":2057730,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba542f1cfafb08831b3d61be59e908943b93ae59","tid":2057730,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:53:24.000Z","msg":"佢下一鋪一定係想攪美國既糧食。可能播毒毒晒美國既農作物"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:59:13.000Z","msg":"......其實真係做得出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:40:59.000Z","msg":"熱戰打唔贏， 一定會用盡所有手段搞到美國內亂半死， 增加自己打贏機會， 亦增加美國開戰成本<br />\n<br />\n武肺，antifa暴亂， 有跡可尋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022c3918a810f10f2425fbdf8d2097cb338a8fe7","tid":2057730,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"957af979120cdd1a3cc2ca098a86cbbf66495a7f","tid":2057730,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba542f1cfafb08831b3d61be59e908943b93ae59","tid":2057730,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:53:24.000Z","msg":"佢下一鋪一定係想攪美國既糧食。可能播毒毒晒美國既農作物"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"咁on9自己切斷自己糧食供應"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"有無睇毛澤東聯俄打美軍個戰略？<br />\n共產黨無當中國人係人"}]}